a slut machine.

19:10.667 --> 19:11.875
(laughing)

19:11.875 --> 19:13.208
Instead of pulling a lever,

19:13.208 --> 19:14.959
you’re pulling on my dong.

19:14.959 --> 19:17.041
Ding-dong. Who’s there?
Will’s there.

19:17.041 --> 19:18.875
I’m sorry, are you Will?

19:18.875 --> 19:20.208
Yeah, man, yeah.

19:20.208 --> 19:22.250
Hey, if there’s a Will,
there’s a way, okay.

19:22.250 --> 19:24.250
Out of her apartment
before she wakes up.

19:24.250 --> 19:26.291
(laughing)

19:26.291 --> 19:28.291
I’m sorry,
that’s just locker room talk.

19:28.291 --> 19:30.166
Yeah, I’m going
to remember you.

19:30.166 --> 19:31.417
Oh.

19:31.417 --> 19:33.000
I’m gonna remember you
as that gross guy

19:33.000 --> 19:34.834
that I met the day
I almost took a job

19:34.834 --> 19:36.333
in the wrong place.

19:36.333 --> 19:38.542
♪

19:38.542 --> 19:39.333
