19:41.166 --> 19:42.709
What?

19:42.709 --> 19:44.542
-I didn’t mean--
COLLEEN: Oh, I’m sorry.

19:45.542 --> 19:46.875
Why are you apologizing?

19:46.875 --> 19:48.834
I’m the one who hit you.

19:48.834 --> 19:51.041
You’re right, I’m sorry.

19:51.041 --> 19:52.250
(chuckling)

19:52.250 --> 19:53.333
I’m Colleen Ortega.

19:53.333 --> 19:54.291
I run HR here.

19:56.000 --> 19:57.000
Matt Short.

19:57.000 --> 20:00.208
COLLEEN: The new--the new guy,
right, of course, um...

20:00.208 --> 20:03.125
It’s really nice to meet you,
Colleen Ortega.

20:03.125 --> 20:04.542
I’m glad to have you aboard.

20:04.542 --> 20:05.667
Thanks, I’m...

20:05.667 --> 20:07.208
♪

